    {
      "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your<strong> chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>free range</strong> <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
