      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped chicken </strong>to a bowl with the <strong>chermoula</strong> and give everything a good mix up, until the chicken is completely coated</p><p>Set aside to marinate</p><p>Chop your <strong>sultanas </strong>roughly</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped sultanas </strong>to a bowl, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> and set them aside to soak</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
