        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and chop your <strong>red onion[s] </strong>into wedges and separate the wedges into petals</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>onion petals </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 5-8 min or until starting to caramelise</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
