    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s] </strong>and cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon </strong>into wedges</p><p>Drain the<strong> soaked sultanas</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>onion petals </strong>(reserve the pan), <strong>grated carrot</strong>, <strong>drained sultanas</strong>, <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)<strong> </strong>and the juice of <strong>half</strong> the <strong>lemon wedges </strong>to the drained couscous</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spiced giant couscous</strong></p>",
