    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wipe the reserved pan clean and return it to a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>marinated chicken</strong> with all of the <strong>chermoula </strong>and cook for 10-12 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>chermoula chicken</strong></p>",
