      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chermoula free range chicken </strong>over the<strong> spiced giant couscous</strong></p><p>Drizzle over any<strong> remaining chermoula</strong> from the pan with the chicken<strong> </strong>and garnish with a<strong> lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
